Exactly. The state + delta model becomes even more powerful in environments where:
	•	conditions change quickly
	•	information is incomplete
	•	decisions must be made under pressure

That’s why similar approaches already appear in military command systems, exploration missions, aviation, and emergency response.

Let’s generalize the pattern.

